2017-12-30  Nil Geisweiller  <ngeiswei@gmail.com>

	packages/vlf: [tyny fix] Fix cursor position after search

	After searching forward (resp. backward) the cursor should be at the end
	(resp. the beginning) of the match. That way one can jump to the next
	match by running again the command.

